    "url": canonical,
    "description": "Built-in luxury Alfresco AXE-30 pizza oven repair across all five SoCal counties. 30-inch gas-fired stone hearth pizza oven manufactured by BBQG Inc. (Commerce, CA). Stone hearth replacement (year 7 to 12 typical, $260 to $560), refractory ceiling insulation rebuild (year 8 to 12, $440 to $780 plus materials), gas valve assembly replacement ($260 to $440), spark electrode and ignition module ($200 to $440). Repair always justified through year 12 to 15 on $4,000 to $8,000 unit. Beverly Hills, Calabasas, Hidden Hills, Newport Coast outdoor kitchen installations. BHGS #A49573 and EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410). $120 outdoor diagnostic.",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
