        <tr><td>Diagnostic (outdoor commercial-tier)</td><td>$120, waived with repair</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Spark electrode replacement</td><td>$200 to $340</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Ignition module replacement</td><td>$260 to $440</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Gas valve assembly replacement</td><td>$260 to $440</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stone hearth replacement</td><td>$260 to $560</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Refractory ceiling insulation rebuild (labor)</td><td>$440 to $780</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Refractory materials (cement, refractory brick)</td><td>$120 to $260</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Door hinge replacement</td><td>$220 to $380</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Door gasket replacement</td><td>$180 to $280</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Annual maintenance visit (full outdoor kitchen suite)</td><td>$120 dx + cleaning service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Year 12-14 multi-component refresh (typical scope)</td><td>$780 to $1,200</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Year 14+ major refresh (gas valve + refractory + hearth)</td><td>$1,400 to $2,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty</td><td>90 days SDAR labor on our work</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 06 WHY US -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">06 · Why AXE owners call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Seven reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Built-in luxury repair specialty.</strong> Refractory rebuilds, gas valve manometer testing, hearth replacement; we do this work week after week on AXE units.</li>
      <li><strong>Annual maintenance contracts on full outdoor kitchen suites.</strong> One $120 dispatch covers diagnostic across grill + AXE + outdoor refrigeration.</li>
      <li><strong>Repair-vs-replace honesty tilted toward repair.</strong> Built-in luxury tier math. We tell you straight when major refresh extends service life 5 to 7 years.</li>
      <li><strong>Combined Alfresco grill + AXE service.</strong> Same parent (BBQG Inc.), same parts pipeline, often same outdoor kitchen install. See our <a href="/outdoor/brands/alfresco/">Alfresco grill page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>BH, Calabasas, Hidden Hills, Newport coverage.</strong> Most AXE density in our service area; we know these installations.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 and EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$120 outdoor diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 07 FAQ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">07 · FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Alfresco AXE repair, common questions.</h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <details class="faq-item">
